When you're with me from now on,

326
00:25:08,000 --> 00:25:10,000
You don't have to pretend to be happy.

327
00:25:11,480 --> 00:25:13,000
However you feel,

328
00:25:13,720 --> 00:25:15,240
Just express your emotions.

329
00:25:16,720 --> 00:25:18,720
If I get mad at you,

330
00:25:19,480 --> 00:25:21,720
Won't you be annoyed with me?

331
00:25:22,480 --> 00:25:23,720
I wouldn't dare do that.

332
00:25:24,480 --> 00:25:25,480
You can do it.

333
00:25:26,720 --> 00:25:28,480
I want you to.

334
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:32,240
When you're annoyed, you should do the same.

335
00:25:33,000 --> 00:25:35,480
When you're annoyed, you should frown.

336
00:25:36,000 --> 00:25:39,000
When you're angry, you should yell.

337
00:25:40,480 --> 00:25:41,480
It's weird.

338
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:44,720
