339
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:46,240
Weird, right?

340
00:25:46,480 --> 00:25:48,720
It will help us to become closer.

341
00:25:49,000 --> 00:25:50,000
Huh?

342
00:25:50,000 --> 00:25:52,000
Sharing negative emotions with each other?

343
00:25:52,000 --> 00:25:54,000
