344
00:25:55,000 --> 00:25:57,000
Positive emotions which are fake,

345
00:25:57,480 --> 00:25:59,720
Will only disappoint in the end.

346
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:03,720
From now on, we share the good and the bad.

347
00:26:04,240 --> 00:26:07,240
This is how we get to know each other better.

348
00:27:51,000 --> 00:27:53,000
If you just want to come back to collect something,

