370
00:29:05,720 --> 00:29:07,720
Did it sound like she wanted to reconcile?

371
00:29:09,480 --> 00:29:10,480
Nueng.

372
00:29:11,480 --> 00:29:13,000
While grandma is still alive,

373
00:29:14,000 --> 00:29:16,000
I won't set foot back here again.

374
00:29:19,000 --> 00:29:21,000
