379
00:30:12,240 --> 00:30:15,480
"Money and fame didn't matter to me."

380
00:30:16,480 --> 00:30:19,240
I would never make a promise like this.

381
00:30:20,000 --> 00:30:23,240
Because I know what is important in my life.

382
00:30:24,240 --> 00:30:26,240
I'll never allow Satan to take it away.

383
00:30:30,000 --> 00:30:32,480
Miss Nueng. Do you know what is important to me?

384
00:30:34,000 --> 00:30:35,480
It's you Miss Nueng.

385
00:30:35,480 --> 00:30:36,480
I love you Miss Nueng.

386
00:30:59,720 --> 00:31:02,240
"Marissa took the initiative"

387
00:31:02,720 --> 00:31:05,000
"Using her instincts to lead"

388
